title: Clean up mess
description: There is a mess. Come clean it up. Make sure you get all of it.

title: Repair a fence
description: The face is broken. You might need your own wood. Make sure you remove the broken parts.

title: Remove trash
description: Trash everywhere. I don't know what happened. There is too much of it for us to clean it up.

title: Cover up graffiti
description: There is an ugly offensive graffiti on the wall. Please remove it. You can paint over it any color. Bring your own paint.
